<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <title>{% block title %}Welcome!{% endblock %}</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="{{ asset('build/front.css') }}">
        {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
        <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{ asset('favicon.ico') }}" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <nav class="navbar navbar-toggleable-md navbar-light bg-faded">
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>

                <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Navbar</a>

                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav">
                        <li class="nav-item active">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="#">Home <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
                        </li>

                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="#">Features</a>
                        </li>

                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="#">Pricing</a>
                        </li>

                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link disabled" href="#">Disabled</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </header>

        {% block body %}{% endblock %}

        <footer>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <p>
                            Pellentesque placerat tincidunt urna, vitae feugiat magna vestibulum non. Mauris ut sagittis est. Pellentesque a felis est. Duis in risus metus. Cras felis ante, sodales eget pretium eu, hendrerit at metus. Maecenas aliquam dictum sapien id ornare.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        {{ render(controller('AppBundle:Front/Article:recentArticles', { 'max': 4 })) }}
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        {{ render(controller('AppBundle:Front/Tags:popular')) }}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>

        {% block javascriptsExternal %}{% endblock %}
        <script type="text/javascript" src="{{ asset('build/front.js') }}"></script>
    </body>
</html>
